## Data Protection

### PII Classification

| Classification | Examples | Storage | Logging |
|---------------|----------|---------|---------|
| Public | Username, avatar URL | Encrypted | Allowed |
| Internal | Email, phone | Encrypted | Hashed/masked |
| Confidential | SSN, credit card, health | AES-256-GCM | NEVER |
| Restricted | Passwords, biometrics | Salted bcrypt | NEVER stored |

### Encryption Standards
- **At rest:** AES-256-GCM with proper IV, keys from KMS/Vault
- **In transit:** TLS 1.3, certificate pinning for mobile, HSTS 1yr+
- **Key rotation:** annually minimum, via KMS dynamic secret engine

### Data Retention
- User data: account duration + 30 days
- Session data: 7 days inactivity
- Audit logs: 2 years
- App logs: 90 days
- Analytics: 1 year (anonymize after 90 days)

